description: Police said the venue was too small for distancing, as the virus takes a toll on German festivities.
title: Coronavirus: Berlin breaks up 600-strong party over Covid
title_page: Coronavirus: Berlin breaks up 600-strong party over Covid - BBC News
maintext: Germany has fared better than the other heavily populated nations in Europe but Sunday was the fourth day in a row that it registered more than 10,000 new cases. The total is now more than 430,000 since the pandemic began.
